00w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_bez_thelotterywinners_boygeorge_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_bez_thelotterywinners_boygeorge_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_bez_thelotterywinners_boygeorge_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_bez_thelotterywinners_boygeorge_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_bez_thelotterywinners_boygeorge_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（12 月 28 日），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bez">贝兹 (Bez</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boy-george">男孩乔治 (Boy George)</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lottery-winners">彩票中奖者</a>一起参加了在曼彻斯特举行的演出。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lottery-winners-interview-kate-nash-row-working-class-arts-koko-album-robbie-williams-3821969">彩票中奖者反思凯特·纳什的争论：“她非常出色地强调了工人阶级在艺术方面缺乏机会”</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队在曼彻斯特学院演奏了他们 2023 年专辑《焦虑替代疗法》中的一系列热门歌曲，其中包括《金钱》，乐队在舞台上用沙球绑住了乐队。他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">《快乐星期一》</a>乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shaun-ryder">肖恩·莱德</a>在该歌曲的专辑版本中演唱。</p><p>后来，男孩乔治加入了他们的歌曲“Let Me Down”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lottery-winners-share-third-single-let-me-down-boy-george-3421846">他也在唱片的单曲中担任主角</a>。您可以在下面观看这两场表演。</p><p>乐队继续演奏了他们最近专辑中的更多歌曲，包括《You&#39;re Not Alone》、《Sertraline》和唱片的主打歌。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">与 Bez 一起庆祝<a href="https://twitter.com/LotteryWinners?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@LotteryWinners</a>专辑排名第一！第一晚很棒，但很特别<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f642.png" alt="🙂" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/y7Xd9I7OEM">pic.twitter.com/y7Xd9I7OEM</a